Package software.web.index.database

Class CropData

  • java.lang.Object
    • software.web.index.database.CropData
  • public class CropData
extends java.lang.Object
    The CropDat retrives the products stored in the database and displays them in multiple pages The User can navigate through these pages and is also given the option to sort the products based on the price or rating.
